# Cloud File Sharing System

A secure cloud-based file sharing application built using Node.js and Express.

## Features

- Upload files
- Download files
- Share files
- Simple UI

## Technologies

- Node.js
- Express.js
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## Installation

```bash
npm install
npm start

